Finding a complete grammar for B has been a challenge.  So I decided
to take a different approach.

The following C grammar is taken from K&R second edition, appendix A.
It is then converted to a form more appropriate for recursive descent
parsing, and then edited to a B grammar.

A.7 Expressions

primary-expression ::= identifier | constant | string | "(" expression ")"

postfix-expression ::=
  primary-expression
  
